Version 1/080509 of FyreVM Help Channel Support (for Glulx only) by Textfyre begins here.Include Version 1 of FyreVM Support by Textfyre.To add the help topic (topic-name - text):	if there is a topic name of topic-name in the Table of Help Topics, stop;	choose a blank row in the Table of Help Topics;	change topic name entry to topic-name.To remove the help topic (topic-name - text):	if there is a topic name of topic-name in the Table of Help Topics:		blank out the whole row.Every turn (this is the write help topics rule):	if the help switch is on:		select the help channel;		say "<help>";		repeat through the Table of Help Topics:			let the topicname be topic name entry;			say "<topic>";			say "[topic name entry]";			say "</topic>";		say "</help>";	select the main channel.Table of Help Topicstopic nametextwith 100 blank rowsFyreVM Help Channel Support ends here.